						               													<description>Valente - O amor em jogo is a storytelling game based on the stories I have created, Vitor Cafaggi, about this young and graceful dog, Valente.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Through the randomness of the cards and using their own skill, reasoning and experience, the players will assemble strips telling the story and the amorous misfortune of the Valiant. Players have the challenge of guiding our hero to the right choice. And what choice is that?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At this point in his life, Valente finds himself in a difficult time. With a platonic love story for Lady and living a recent passion with Princess, he finds himself in a bind, not knowing which of the two to give his heart. In the game, this is the scenario. You and the other players will help Valente make that decision, but that path will not be easy.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;According to the created stories, you will guide Valente's heart as he hears the invaluable advice of his best friend Bu, plays RPG with his friends, takes his little sister to the ballet and devours roast beef sandwiches!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
